[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.4,
    "text": "Seems like something terrible happened here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.6,
    "endTime": 3.6,
    "text": "Can you help us?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.8,
    "endTime": 6.699999999999999,
    "text": "Our planet was taken over by some kind of... entity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.9,
    "endTime": 9.9,
    "text": "The people it takes over, they look like your friends, your family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 12.5,
    "text": "But they're not themselves anymore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.7,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "They're part of... it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 16.0,
    "text": "Hello, Rick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.0,
    "endTime": 18.0,
    "text": "Long time no see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 19.0,
    "text": "Unity?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.0,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "Summer, Morty, this is, uh, Unity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.3,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "We sort of used to, uh... date."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.4,
    "endTime": 27.0,
    "text": "I could do whatever you do and more, baby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "Quite an operation you got going here, Yoon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 32.3,
    "text": "You're a whole planet now, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.5,
    "endTime": 35.5,
    "text": "After we broke up, I spent some time wandering through space."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.7,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "Then I found this world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 40.4,
    "text": "Where I was better able to focus on my passion for unification."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.5,
    "endTime": 42.0,
    "text": "You mean stealing people's bodies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.3,
    "endTime": 43.4,
    "text": "Summer, rude."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.5,
    "endTime": 44.7,
    "text": "So, what's next?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.9,
    "endTime": 50.199999999999996,
    "text": "After I become a Type 1 civilization, this world will be invited into the Galactic Federation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.4,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "Oh, goody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.2,
    "endTime": 54.300000000000004,
    "text": "From there, I'll have access to countless planets and species."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.5,
    "endTime": 56.3,
    "text": "One by one, I will unify them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.5,
    "endTime": 57.8,
    "text": "I will become the universe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 60.4,
    "text": "And I will be what the single-minded once called a god."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.6,
    "endTime": 61.800000000000004,
    "text": "Oh, that's pretty sexy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 63.6,
    "text": "Hey, listen, where can we get a drink around here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.8,
    "endTime": 66.3,
    "text": "Recreational substances were phased out here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.5,
    "endTime": 69.3,
    "text": "There's no need for escape from the self when your world is one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.4,
    "endTime": 71.7,
    "text": "Unity, Unity, who am I talking to?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.9,
    "endTime": 75.60000000000001,
    "text": "I watched you assimilate a whole police station just to get your hands on the evidence locker."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.8,
    "endTime": 80.5,
    "text": "Rick, when we met, I was a young hive mind with the population of a small town."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.7,
    "endTime": 81.8,
    "text": "People change."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry to disappoint you, but I've grown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "Hey, listen, I've grown too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 88.0,
    "text": "I have!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.0,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "You see, I've reconnected with my family, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 91.0,
    "text": "Hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.0,
    "endTime": 92.3,
    "text": "Why is that, I wonder?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.5,
    "endTime": 93.6,
    "text": "Maybe it's part of getting old."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "Maybe I just miss being with a collective."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "Yes, Rick, yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "Oh, yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.8,
    "endTime": 104.6,
    "text": "Do you know what I love about you, Rick?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.8,
    "endTime": 108.5,
    "text": "You're the only single mind I've met that really sees the big picture."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.7,
    "endTime": 109.5,
    "text": "You got that right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.7,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "But, baby, listen, you're talking about taking over planets and galaxies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.0,
    "endTime": 116.5,
    "text": "You gotta just remember to let go sometimes, you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.7,
    "endTime": 117.5,
    "text": "I can let go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.7,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "Hey, look!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.3,
    "endTime": 119.3,
    "text": "You see that town across the river?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.6,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "Watch this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "Woah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.0,
    "endTime": 123.5,
    "text": "Woah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.7,
    "endTime": 124.0,
    "text": "That's not what I meant!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "It's okay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "It's okay, I evacuated!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.3,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "I evacuated the town, look!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "Hey, we're right here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "We're fine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "Oh, that was awesome!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "My grandkids weren't in that town, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "Are my grandkids alive?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.3,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "Steven, set yourself free!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.0,
    "endTime": 151.3,
    "text": "Summer, before I took over this planet, this man was a registered sex offender."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.5,
    "endTime": 154.3,
    "text": "I have transformed life here into a paradise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.5,
    "endTime": 156.5,
    "text": "Prostitutes are now scientists."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.8,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "The homeless are now physosophers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 161.6,
    "text": "Oh, oh, physosophers? Nice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.8,
    "endTime": 164.5,
    "text": "Oh my god, where did you learn to talk, you grandpa-stealing slut?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.7,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "I'm feeling..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.0,
    "endTime": 172.0,
    "text": "Oh man, let me help all of you guys up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.0,
    "endTime": 173.5,
    "text": "I'm fine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.7,
    "endTime": 175.2,
    "text": "I think you're getting what you wanted, Summer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.4,
    "endTime": 177.6,
    "text": "Something's happening to Unity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.8,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "Do all of you remember who you are?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 182.8,
    "text": "Yeah, my name is Ron Benson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 192.0,
    "text": "I'm an electrical engineer, father of two, and as you can see from my flat, concentric nipple rings, I'm a member of this planet's top race!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.1,
    "endTime": 194.2,
    "text": "The Cone Nipple people will rule this world!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.4,
    "endTime": 196.6,
    "text": "You shut your mouth, you dirty knife nipple bastards!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.8,
    "endTime": 199.5,
    "text": "What'd you say to me, you target chest piece of shit?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.7,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "Race war!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.0,
    "endTime": 206.5,
    "text": "Hey, these two freaks have no race!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.7,
    "endTime": 208.5,
    "text": "Hello, Summer. Hello, Morty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.5,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "It's okay, you're safe now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.2,
    "endTime": 211.0,
    "text": "Unity?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.0,
    "endTime": 212.0,
    "text": "I am so sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.2,
    "endTime": 215.0,
    "text": "I didn't know freedom meant people doing stuff that sucks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.2,
    "endTime": 218.0,
    "text": "I was thinking more of a choose-your-own-cellphone-carrier thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.2,
    "endTime": 219.7,
    "text": "Aw, Summer, you did nothing wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.9,
    "endTime": 221.5,
    "text": "I'm having fun with your grandpa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.7,
    "endTime": 225.0,
    "text": "Grandpa, we need to go home. Now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.0,
    "endTime": 226.0,
    "text": "See ya."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.5,
    "endTime": 227.0,
    "text": "We're not leaving without you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.0,
    "endTime": 227.0,
    "text": "Oh my god, you guys, I get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.0,
    "endTime": 231.0,
    "text": "You're afraid the big, bad hive mind is gonna steal your grandpa away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.0,
    "endTime": 231.0,
    "text": "Actually, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.0,
    "endTime": 235.0,
    "text": "I think Unity's great and you're a horrible influence on it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.0,
    "endTime": 237.0,
    "text": "Up next, are you a concerned grandchild or just a buzzkill?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "We'll tell you how you can know for sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.0,
    "endTime": 242.0,
    "text": "I think you two are a little outnumbered."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.0,
    "endTime": 244.0,
    "text": "Is there a way for you to call Summer and Morty?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.0,
    "endTime": 247.0,
    "text": "I feel bad that they— Screw those guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 249.0,
    "text": "Don't waste your brain on those weirdos, Unity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.0,
    "endTime": 252.0,
    "text": "They're no different from any of the aimless chumps that you occupy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 258.0,
    "text": "They just put you at the center of their lives because you're powerful, and then because they put you there, they want you to be less powerful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.8,
    "endTime": 259.0,
    "text": "Never gonna happen, though, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.0,
    "endTime": 260.0,
    "text": "Back in a flash."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.0,
    "endTime": 260.0,
    "text": "Hey, Yoon!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.0,
    "endTime": 270.0,
    "text": "You got any more—"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.0,
    "endTime": 274.0,
    "text": "Rick, forgive me for doing this in notes. I'm not strong enough to do it in persons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.0,
    "endTime": 277.0,
    "text": "I realize now that I'm attracted to you for the same reason I can't be with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.0,
    "endTime": 278.0,
    "text": "You can't change."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.8,
    "endTime": 283.0,
    "text": "And I have no problem with that, but it clearly means I have a problem with myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.8,
    "endTime": 286.0,
    "text": "I'm sure there's no perfect version of me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.0,
    "endTime": 290.0,
    "text": "I'm sure I'll just unify species after species and never really be complete."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.0,
    "endTime": 293.0,
    "text": "But I know how it goes with us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.0,
    "endTime": 295.0,
    "text": "I lose who I am and become part of you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.0,
    "endTime": 299.0,
    "text": "Because in a strange way, you're better at what I do without even trying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.0,
    "endTime": 299.0,
    "text": "Yours."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.0,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "And nobody else's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.0,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "Unity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.0,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "Unity!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.0,
    "endTime": 302.0,
    "text": "Unity!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.0,
    "endTime": 308.0,
    "text": "How can I assist you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.0,
    "endTime": 311.0,
    "text": "I want to talk to— Unity!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.0,
    "endTime": 316.0,
    "text": "You are classified as a hostile entity, and Unity doesn't want to talk to— This isn't gonna shake out like you think, pal!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.0,
    "endTime": 318.0,
    "text": "Unity's not into other hive minds!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.0,
    "endTime": 323.0,
    "text": "It's gonna suck you in and use you up, and a month from now, I'm gonna be making out with all of you in a bunch of red wigs!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.0,
    "endTime": 323.0,
    "text": "Unity!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.0,
    "endTime": 323.0,
    "text": "Unity!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.0,
    "endTime": 323.0,
    "text": "Unity!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.0,
    "endTime": 327.0,
    "text": "I know you can hear me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.0,
    "endTime": 328.0,
    "text": "Get out here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.0,
    "endTime": 328.0,
    "text": "Weapon systems engaged."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.0,
    "endTime": 330.0,
    "text": "Oh, in your dreams you have weapon systems."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.0,
    "endTime": 333.0,
    "text": "Rick, you said we were going to a movie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.0,
    "endTime": 334.0,
    "text": "We are, Morty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.0,
    "endTime": 336.0,
    "text": "You just got saved by the bell, bitch!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.0,
    "endTime": 336.0,
    "text": "Okay, let's do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.0,
    "endTime": 337.0,
    "text": "Therapy me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.0,
    "endTime": 341.0,
    "text": "Maybe we should turn off the phone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.0,
    "endTime": 342.0,
    "text": "President of the United States?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.0,
    "endTime": 344.0,
    "text": "Thought you might think that was cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.0,
    "endTime": 345.0,
    "text": "You like it when people think you're cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.0,
    "endTime": 348.0,
    "text": "You're extra analytical today, looking to remodel your kitchen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.0,
    "endTime": 350.0,
    "text": "We've got a situation in the state of Virginia."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.0,
    "endTime": 353.0,
    "text": "Virginia has declared itself literally and exclusively for lovers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.0,
    "endTime": 357.0,
    "text": "As you can see, Virginia has no crime, no poverty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.0,
    "endTime": 359.0,
    "text": "All goods are freely given."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.0,
    "endTime": 360.0,
    "text": "What happened?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.0,
    "endTime": 361.0,
    "text": "Tell me the secret."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.0,
    "endTime": 363.0,
    "text": "Well, if I tell you, you'll tell everyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.0,
    "endTime": 366.0,
    "text": "But if I show you, you won't have to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.0,
    "endTime": 367.0,
    "text": "How unsettling and cryptic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.0,
    "endTime": 373.0,
    "text": "Sir, it's some kind of body-snatching hive mind!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.0,
    "endTime": 374.0,
    "text": "Pick up your phone, asshole."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.0,
    "endTime": 379.0,
    "text": "When I call, it's an actual emergency."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.0,
    "endTime": 379.0,
    "text": "Rick?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.0,
    "endTime": 380.0,
    "text": "Unity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.0,
    "endTime": 380.0,
    "text": "Take it easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.0,
    "endTime": 383.0,
    "text": "Take it easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384.0,
    "endTime": 386.0,
    "text": "I can explain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.0,
    "endTime": 388.0,
    "text": "Just let me get things under control."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.0,
    "endTime": 390.0,
    "text": "You controlling things is the explanation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.0,
    "endTime": 393.0,
    "text": "And we agreed you wouldn't do it where I work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.0,
    "endTime": 395.0,
    "text": "What the fuck are you playing me with?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.0,
    "endTime": 397.0,
    "text": "New scent I picked up after you left."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.0,
    "endTime": 398.0,
    "text": "I call it scent of love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.0,
    "endTime": 399.0,
    "text": "You concocted a me-repellent?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.0,
    "endTime": 402.0,
    "text": "Does that look like a bad idea?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.0,
    "endTime": 407.0,
    "text": "Rick, are you in a relationship with the population of Virginia?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.0,
    "endTime": 407.0,
    "text": "We dated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.0,
    "endTime": 408.0,
    "text": "Calm down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.0,
    "endTime": 411.0,
    "text": "We came because we're worried about you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.0,
    "endTime": 412.0,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.0,
    "endTime": 413.0,
    "text": "We hear things, Rick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.0,
    "endTime": 418.0,
    "text": "I tried calling, but is it true you're looking for him again?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 418.0,
    "endTime": 419.0,
    "text": "That's none of your business."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.0,
    "endTime": 421.0,
    "text": "You're our business."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.0,
    "endTime": 424.0,
    "text": "You quit that business, and you're fired from that business."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424.0,
    "endTime": 428.0,
    "text": "And I'm using your last paycheck to cover the stapler you stole, which was my heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.0,
    "endTime": 429.0,
    "text": "Civil war, baby!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 429.0,
    "endTime": 433.0,
    "text": "It's time to put these bastards on ice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.0,
    "endTime": 434.0,
    "text": "Queue up the dome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434.0,
    "endTime": 435.0,
    "text": "Ow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.0,
    "endTime": 443.0,
    "text": "A nation in turmoil tonight as the entire state of Virginia continues to be trapped inside an energy dome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.0,
    "endTime": 447.0,
    "text": "Mr. President, you cut eight million pieces of me off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447.0,
    "endTime": 448.0,
    "text": "It hurt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.0,
    "endTime": 448.0,
    "text": "Boo-hoo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.0,
    "endTime": 451.0,
    "text": "I've made it clear we can't be friends, Rick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.0,
    "endTime": 454.0,
    "text": "But I need to reconnect those people so I can properly release them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.0,
    "endTime": 455.0,
    "text": "They're hosting a mindless collective."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.0,
    "endTime": 459.0,
    "text": "If it connects to another mind, it could become its own colony."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.0,
    "endTime": 461.0,
    "text": "You ghosted me to focus on your work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.0,
    "endTime": 463.0,
    "text": "Your work is absorbing the universe, but it's my universe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.0,
    "endTime": 464.0,
    "text": "Please go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.0,
    "endTime": 467.0,
    "text": "We'll spray the Virginians before they touch anyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.0,
    "endTime": 471.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry you lost a finger, but that's the price of surprise butt play."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.0,
    "endTime": 471.0,
    "text": "Goodbye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.0,
    "endTime": 471.0,
    "text": "Goodbye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.0,
    "endTime": 472.0,
    "text": "Alien vessel is departing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.0,
    "endTime": 473.0,
    "text": "Good job, people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 473.0,
    "endTime": 478.0,
    "text": "I'll run the aerosol cannon from the chopper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.0,
    "endTime": 479.0,
    "text": "We need the operator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479.0,
    "endTime": 481.0,
    "text": "Arriving at the dome, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.0,
    "endTime": 481.0,
    "text": "Good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.0,
    "endTime": 484.0,
    "text": "Just gonna see how we're looking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 484.0,
    "endTime": 492.0,
    "text": "And there's Helicopter One with the aforementioned gas, and you can actually see President Curtis inside, checking his phone to see if this will make people like him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.0,
    "endTime": 498.0,
    "text": "Fact is, nothing short of literally a 100% approval rating is gonna save Curtis in the next election."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.0,
    "endTime": 498.0,
    "text": "100% approval."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.0,
    "endTime": 498.0,
    "text": "Whoopsie!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.0,
    "endTime": 499.0,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.0,
    "endTime": 500.0,
    "text": "Sir?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500.0,
    "endTime": 505.0,
    "text": "I just gotta get the thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.0,
    "endTime": 506.0,
    "text": "How is that gonna work?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 506.0,
    "endTime": 507.0,
    "text": "Give it to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.0,
    "endTime": 509.0,
    "text": "Give me that hive!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.0,
    "endTime": 509.0,
    "text": "Holy shit!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.0,
    "endTime": 510.0,
    "text": "Hello, sir!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.0,
    "endTime": 511.0,
    "text": "The President has saved us!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.0,
    "endTime": 524.0,
    "text": "He's going to assimilate the Earth faster than I can fight it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.0,
    "endTime": 526.0,
    "text": "And you want me to talk to him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.0,
    "endTime": 527.0,
    "text": "There's no talking to him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.0,
    "endTime": 529.0,
    "text": "No human mind can keep itself together while controlling millions of people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529.0,
    "endTime": 530.0,
    "text": "So where are we going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 530.0,
    "endTime": 534.0,
    "text": "I need Unity's help, so you need to convince her I'm worth it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.0,
    "endTime": 534.0,
    "text": "You aren't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.0,
    "endTime": 535.0,
    "text": "So lie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.0,
    "endTime": 541.0,
    "text": "Look, it's clear you weren't lying when you said you could've taken over Earth because your finger just took over America."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.0,
    "endTime": 543.0,
    "text": "I need you to help me fix that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 543.0,
    "endTime": 545.0,
    "text": "Oh, it took that to make you believe me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.0,
    "endTime": 547.0,
    "text": "Why should I believe you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 547.0,
    "endTime": 548.0,
    "text": "You show up unannounced and hijack a state."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.0,
    "endTime": 549.0,
    "text": "I called you multiple times!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 549.0,
    "endTime": 550.0,
    "text": "You ghosted me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 550.0,
    "endTime": 552.0,
    "text": "Rick, is that true?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552.0,
    "endTime": 554.0,
    "text": "She dumped me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.0,
    "endTime": 556.0,
    "text": "Why would I answer her calls?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.0,
    "endTime": 559.0,
    "text": "Alright, I'm going to commit a cardinal sin in couples therapy here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.0,
    "endTime": 560.0,
    "text": "But Rick, I think you're wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.0,
    "endTime": 562.0,
    "text": "Bringing you is a mistake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.0,
    "endTime": 569.0,
    "text": "You had an outer space lady who was worried for your life and your response was hostile enough to cause a huge problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.0,
    "endTime": 570.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 570.0,
    "endTime": 574.0,
    "text": "Now you're asking her to both forgive you and solve it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 574.0,
    "endTime": 579.0,
    "text": "Unity, I think the reason Rick brought me here is that he doesn't know how to indicate to you he's changed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.0,
    "endTime": 581.0,
    "text": "Because he's changing very slowly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581.0,
    "endTime": 581.0,
    "text": "But he is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581.0,
    "endTime": 586.0,
    "text": "Alright, anyone else want to call me a baby?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 586.0,
    "endTime": 589.0,
    "text": "Maybe we can drag this out until Earth is fully assimilated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.0,
    "endTime": 589.0,
    "text": "Alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.0,
    "endTime": 591.0,
    "text": "So you're asking for an invasion?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.0,
    "endTime": 591.0,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.0,
    "endTime": 593.0,
    "text": "Hold them back!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.0,
    "endTime": 594.0,
    "text": "They love me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 594.0,
    "endTime": 599.0,
    "text": "They just forgot!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.0,
    "endTime": 599.0,
    "text": "They just forgot!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.0,
    "endTime": 600.0,
    "text": "They just forgot!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.0,
    "endTime": 600.0,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.0,
    "endTime": 601.0,
    "text": "Stop!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601.0,
    "endTime": 602.0,
    "text": "You love me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 602.0,
    "endTime": 602.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 602.0,
    "endTime": 605.0,
    "text": "Why are you stopping?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.0,
    "endTime": 607.0,
    "text": "I've won you over?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.0,
    "endTime": 609.0,
    "text": "Oh, good!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.0,
    "endTime": 609.0,
    "text": "You're here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.0,
    "endTime": 609.0,
    "text": "Unity!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.0,
    "endTime": 614.0,
    "text": "Kept them warm for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 614.0,
    "endTime": 617.0,
    "text": "They went a little crazy, but uh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 617.0,
    "endTime": 619.0,
    "text": "Anyway, seems like this is all over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 619.0,
    "endTime": 621.0,
    "text": "Helen, we could grab some coffee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.0,
    "endTime": 622.0,
    "text": "Wait, Unity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 622.0,
    "endTime": 623.0,
    "text": "What are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 623.0,
    "endTime": 624.0,
    "text": "Alright, Rick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.0,
    "endTime": 624.0,
    "text": "That's everyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.0,
    "endTime": 625.0,
    "text": "Nice job, Yun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.0,
    "endTime": 630.0,
    "text": "Well, this has been quite a session."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.0,
    "endTime": 632.0,
    "text": "Hope you do group discounts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.0,
    "endTime": 635.0,
    "text": "Actually, just send the bill to the White House."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 636.0,
    "endTime": 638.0,
    "text": "I wouldn't be doing this for anyone else, Rick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 638.0,
    "endTime": 641.0,
    "text": "Yeah, it was nice to team up again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.0,
    "endTime": 643.0,
    "text": "No, I mean I wouldn't be doing it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643.0,
    "endTime": 646.0,
    "text": "I've never released hundreds of millions of people before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.0,
    "endTime": 648.0,
    "text": "This is gonna suck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 648.0,
    "endTime": 648.0,
    "text": "Rick..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 648.0,
    "endTime": 649.0,
    "text": "Here, it's over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 649.0,
    "endTime": 650.0,
    "text": "Nice job, Yun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 650.0,
    "endTime": 650.0,
    "text": "I'm fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 662.0,
    "endTime": 667.0,
    "text": "You want a painkiller?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 668.0,
    "endTime": 671.0,
    "text": "I'm on a few of them right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 671.0,
    "endTime": 673.0,
    "text": "No, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.0,
    "endTime": 675.0,
    "text": "I mean, you can hang out if you want."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 676.0,
    "endTime": 677.0,
    "text": "Come see the kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 677.0,
    "endTime": 677.0,
    "text": "I trust you now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 677.0,
    "endTime": 682.0,
    "text": "That's nice, but I don't trust you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682.0,
    "endTime": 682.0,
    "text": "Fair enough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 683.0,
    "endTime": 683.0,
    "text": "Hey, Rick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 683.0,
    "endTime": 684.0,
    "text": "It's Unity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 684.0,
    "endTime": 689.0,
    "text": "Give me a call, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 694.0,
    "endTime": 708.0,
    "text": "Hey, Rick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 708.0,
    "endTime": 709.0,
    "text": "Unity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 709.0,
    "endTime": 711.0,
    "text": "Look, cards on the table."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 711.0,
    "endTime": 715.0,
    "text": "I heard you were going after that guy again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 715.0,
    "endTime": 715.0,
    "text": "Just made me worried."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 715.0,
    "endTime": 716.0,
    "text": "Give me a call."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716.0,
    "endTime": 718.0,
    "text": "Look, I get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.0,
    "endTime": 719.0,
    "text": "I dumped you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 719.0,
    "endTime": 720.0,
    "text": "You're ignoring me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 720.0,
    "endTime": 723.0,
    "text": "But I care about you, and I just want to know you're alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 723.0,
    "endTime": 724.0,
    "text": "Hey, Rick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.0,
    "endTime": 725.0,
    "text": "Listen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.0,
    "endTime": 727.0,
    "text": "I'm just gonna stop by Virginia, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 727.0,
    "endTime": 732.0,
    "text": "I don't know what state you live in, but I'll camp out there and try to reach you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 732.0,
    "endTime": 732.0,
    "text": "Hope you're okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 732.0,
    "endTime": 733.0,
    "text": "You"
  }
]